# googleforms_sheet_values (Data Source)

Reads a bounded A1 range of values from a Google Spreadsheet.



<!-- schema generated by tfplugindocs -->
## Schema

### Required

- `range` (String) A1 range to read, e.g. `Config!A1:D20`.
- `spreadsheet_id` (String) Spreadsheet ID.

### Read-Only

- `rows` (Attributes List) Rows returned from the API. Each row is an object containing `cells` (list of strings). (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--rows))

<a id="nestedatt--rows"></a>
### Nested Schema for `rows`

Read-Only:

- `cells` (List of String) The cells in this row.
